* 2013-04-30 2.0
- Added "only_from" option, to limit the locations allowed to access a service
- Added "redirect" option, to redirect a port to a different port on the same or another computer
- Uses Puppet's service management now (rather than /etc/init.d/xinetd)
- Improved documentation
- First version maintained by Alex Lowe <amlowe@ieee.org>
- Removed outdated LICENSE file that referenced GPLv2

* 2012-06-07 1.1.0
- Add port and bind options to services
- make services deletable

1.0.1 - 20100812
    * added documentation

1.0.0 - 20100624
    * initial release
